summary:
This is a major update. New hair, I have changed a bit the faces. All new files.
Now with optional location Dragonsreach by a request. 7Base, 7Base TBBP HDT, ADEC no Tattoos, ADEC TBBP no Tattoos, CBBE, CBBE TBBP, UNPB and UNPB BBP Bodyoptions.s.
descriptionHtml:
[img]http://i.imgur.com/4BdpPVY.jpg[/img][font=Georgia][size=3][b]
[i][color=Cyan]This is a major update. New hair, I have changed a bit the faces. All new files. 7Base, ADEC, CBBE and UNPB Bodyoptions.[/color][/i]
[i][color=Cyan]Now with optional location Dragonsreach by a request. 7Base, 7Base TBBP HDT, ADEC, ADEC TBBP, CBBE, CBBE TBBP, UNPB and UNPB BBP Bodyoptions.[/color][/i][/b][/size][/font]
[font=Georgia][size=3][b]
[i][color=DeepSkyBlue]This is a Standalone Mod[/color][/i][/b][/size][/font]


[font=Georgia][size=3][b][i][color=DeepSkyBlue]Locations:[/color][/i][/b][/size][/font]
[img]http://i.imgur.com/nCVWwoJ.jpg[/img]
[font=Georgia][size=3][b][i][color=Cyan]Alexaa Axe-Barbarien/Levl.8: You find Alexaa in Whiterun,HonningbrewMeadery.[/color][/i][/b][/size][/font]
[img]http://i.imgur.com/gAYW2hc.jpg[/img][font=Georgia][size=3][b]
[i][color=Cyan]Ayaahna Ayha-Rouge/Levl.8:You find Ayaahna in Whiterun, Warmaidens .[/color][/i][/b][/size][/font]
[img]http://i.imgur.com/aoycrca.jpg[/img]
[font=Georgia][size=3][b][i][color=Cyan]Ayleen Ale -Shaman/Levl.7::You find Ayleen in Riverwood,SleepingGiantInn.[/color][/i][/b][/size][/font]

[font=Georgia][size=4][b][i][color=DeepSkyBlue]Recommend:[/color][/i][/b][/size][/font]

[i][color=RoyalBlue][font=Georgia][size=3][b]For All BBP_TBBP Versions: These body options do have extra requirements refer to those mod pages if you need extra help
-NOTE: To run any BBP/TBBP-Body version Mod properly, you have to install a skeleton which supports BBP or TBBP such as XP32's XP32 Maximum Skeleton, which is what i have used. If not you'll get a crash at startup.
There are several skeleton/animation/package options out there to choose from.[/b][/size][/font]
[/color][/i]
[font=Georgia][size=4][i][b][color=Cyan]Does not replace anything in Game!![/color][/b][/i][/size][/font][b]
